column5: Well I'm on the hunt for some furniture, picked up a sweet old harvest table from someone in Kitchener this evening, now I'm needing some chairs so I've been combing kijiji as chairs from a store are pretty expensive when you need 6 of them haha.  I came across this and I'm awaiting a reply, but I'm not too optimistic as the ad was posted 6 weeks ago and only $200 for the 6 of them, regardless I'd like to try and find some like them, and with a group like there is here I'm sure someone might be able to point me in the right direction    Thanks!
Cool, ends up they're still available  no need to go on a hunt lol
Cool, ends up they're still available  no need to go on a hunt lol Good luck as they do look nice.
Just picked them up best $200 I've spent! This whole moving thing ain't cheap lol
They look good and congrats.  moving is never easy and or cheap...
